column2: Aaja Meri Barbad Mohabbat Ke Sahare
Socha Tha Kya Kya Ho Gaya
Milte Hi Ankhen Dil Hua Deewana
Ae Husn Zara Jaag Tujhe Ishq
Chale Aaj Tum Jahan Se (O Door Ke Musafir)
Koi Sagar Dil Ko Bahlata Nahin
Dil Ki Mehfil Saji Hai Chale Aaiye
Kal Raat Zindagi Se Mulaqat Ho Gayi
Aaj Sakhi Ri More Piya Ghar Aayere
Dheere Dheere Bol Koi Sun Lega
Dukh Bhare Din Beete Re Bhaiya
Mere Paas Aao Nazar To Milao
Yeh Dil Ki Lagi Kya Hogi
Chandan Ka Palna Resham Ko Dori
Tere Husn Ki Kya Tarif Karun
Jhoole Mein Pawan Ki Aai Bahar
Dekh Liya Maine Kismat Ka Tamasha
Yaad Mein Teri Jaag Jaag Ke Hum
Tan Rang Lo Ji Aaj Mann Ranglo
